# Proxy endpoint vars (http_proxy, no_proxy, …) live in docker-compose.yml's
# x-sandbox-proxy-env anchor, not here: they embed the per-session ${SANDBOX_IP},
# which Compose interpolates in `environment:` but NOT inside an env_file. Only the
# static CA path remains, shared by the app and the dependency-fetch hardener.
NODE_EXTRA_CA_CERTS=/etc/squid/ssl_cert/ca-cert.pem
